name: Movers Corp
tag_list: movers, moving, labor, laborer, service, storage, transport, move
overview:
Movers Corp is an online marketplace of local moving companies, labor providers and storage facilities.

Movers Corp allows consumers to search for the local moving company or labor provider that is more appropriate for their needs and budget. Simply by entering a zip code and the desired moving day, a full list of local movers will be presented to compare their moving prices side by side. Moreover, vital information such as moving insurance and licensing will be prominently displayed to consider as well. And something that is also an important factor when it comes to selecting one company or the other such as reviews provided by past customers will be made available, too.

Consumers are actually capable of placing a moving order through the site - there is no need to leave the site in order to book any of the featured companies. If all goes well, you will receive an order confirmation and be contacted within 24 hours in order to verify everything, and also to provide some final details and information.
